reviewText: I have not viewed this entire tape, but I was disappointed three times in the first 40 minutes when it did not play as great as the seller indicated and the picture became distorted for a few seconds.
As promised and in good shape.
Have been looking for Jacki Sorensen's workout for a while now.  So glad to have found it.  A good, solid work-out without feeling like you've been run over by a truck the next day.
This video tape is just what I was looking for since the classes have gotten so expensive.  The dances are easy to learn and fun to do and the music is also what I was looking for.

this tape marked the beginning of aerobics, as we know today.  although some of the songs and moves are outdated, it is still a good work-out, especially for us "oldies but goodies"  If a copy can be found, grab it. It is fun and energetic.
